  exit 3  Read-only mode active (--read-only / IB_READ_ONLY) → persisted switch is blocked under read-only; use the per-command global --company <id> ephemeral context
  exit 2 (HTTP 401)  Token expired          → ib auth refresh
  exit 6 (HTTP 500)  Backend error          → retry with --verbose

NOTES
