ERRORS (stderr, exit non-zero)
  exit 3 (HTTP 403)  Not a system admin     → use a system-admin token
  exit 5 (HTTP 404)  Not a draft / not found → only status='draft' rows are deletable; non-draft or missing id → 404
  exit 2 (HTTP 401)  Token expired          → ib auth refresh
