  exit 6 (HTTP 500)  Backend error          → retry with --verbose

EXAMPLES
  ib jerry admin request-expire 41 --reason "abandoned"
"
`;

exports[`Help snapshots — contract stability > help for ib jerry admin request-get matches snapshot 1`] = `
"USAGE
  ib jerry admin request-get <requestId> [flags]

DESCRIPTION
  One request's full detail — date, customer, placing operator, worksite, m³, status, offer count, accepted/best price (GET /api/admin/jerry-requests/:id). For the offers use \`ib jerry admin request-offers\`. System-admin only.
  Permissions: requires isSystemAdmin.

ARGUMENTS
  <requestId> NUMBER    pumppuRequestId (required)

FLAGS
  (none)

GLOBAL FLAGS
