OUTPUT (JSON, stdout)
  { pumppuRequestId, status, createdAt, sentAt, expiresAt, totalM3, kayttokohde, customerAsiakasId, customerNimi, operatorName, osoite, offerCount, acceptedPriceCents, bestPriceCents }

ERRORS (stderr, exit non-zero)
  exit 4 (HTTP 400)  Invalid id             → pass a numeric requestId
  exit 3 (HTTP 403)  Not a system admin     → use a system-admin token
  exit 5 (HTTP 404)  Request not found      → verify pumppuRequestId
  exit 2 (HTTP 401)  Token expired          → ib auth refresh
  exit 6 (HTTP 500)  Backend error          → retry with --verbose

EXAMPLES
