OUTPUT (JSON, stdout)
  ListEnvelope<{documentId, typeName, version, title, status, effectiveDate, createdBy, createdTime, notes, ownerAsiakasId}>

ERRORS (stderr, exit non-zero)
  exit 2 (HTTP 401)  Token expired          → ib auth refresh
  exit 6 (HTTP 500)  Backend error          → retry with --verbose

SEE ALSO
