OUTPUT (JSON, stdout)
  { totalSlowQueries, bufferedQueries, avgDuration, maxDuration, minDuration, topProcedures:[{ name, count, avgMs }], byEntity, since, threshold, sentryThreshold, environment }

ERRORS (stderr, exit non-zero)
  exit 2 (HTTP 401)  Token expired          → ib auth refresh
  exit 3 (HTTP 403)  Not a developer        → requires isSystemAdmin or isDeveloper
  exit 6 (HTTP 500)  Backend error          → retry with --verbose

NOTES
  - SQL durations cover the executeQuery (cache-runner) path only — raw getConnection() queries are not timed.

SEE ALSO
  ib perf slow, ib perf config

EXAMPLES
