DESCRIPTION
  Change-tracker audit trail for one vehicle — who changed which field, when, old→new, with --reason. Alias of \`ib log entity vehicle\`. For DRIVER-assignment history use \`ib vehicle drivers\` (different data: personPvm assignments). GET /api/changes/vehicle/:vehicleId/:ownerAsiakasId.
  Auth: requires login (any authenticated user).

ARGUMENTS
