exports[`Help snapshots — contract stability > help for ib worksite log matches snapshot 1`] = `
"USAGE
  ib worksite log <tyomaaId> [flags]

DESCRIPTION
  Change-tracker audit trail for one worksite (tyomaa) — who changed which field, when, old→new, with --reason. Alias of \`ib log entity tyomaa\`. GET /api/changes/tyomaa/:tyomaaId/:ownerAsiakasId.
  Auth: requires login (any authenticated user).

ARGUMENTS
  <tyomaaId> NUMBER    tyomaaId (required)

FLAGS
